From: Steven Rostedt <rostedt@goodmis.org>
Date: Thu, 20 Feb 2025 15:20:11 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] ftrace: Do not add duplicate entries in subops manager ops
References: bsc#1234429
Patch-mainline: 6.12.17
Git-commit: 8eb4b09e0bbd30981305643229fe7640ad41b667

commit 8eb4b09e0bbd30981305643229fe7640ad41b667 upstream.

Check if a function is already in the manager ops of a subops. A manager
ops contains multiple subops, and if two or more subops are tracing the
same function, the manager ops only needs a single entry in its hash.

